288
00:11:41,679 --> 00:11:43,240
There's no way she'd like a goofball like Li Wai.

289
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:44,480
Right?

290
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:57,000
Miss, let me tell you the truth.

291
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,559
I'm not the person you're supposed to meet.

292
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,480
That guy is no good.

293
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:02,120
He hired me to act crazy and drive you away.

294
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:04,480
But I don't know how to act crazy, right?

295
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,120
Look, you're such a catch.

296
00:12:06,559 --> 00:12:07,919
Age anxiety isn't a problem.

297
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,480
Why are you in such a rush to get married?

298
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,200
Miss, you've misunderstood.

299
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,600
I'm not what you think.

300
00:12:18,679 --> 00:12:19,600
I'm not a bad person.

301
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,320
You... believe me, I didn't...

302
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,399
Get in here!

303
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,320
Police!

304
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,240
Squat down!

305
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:29,720
All men, don't move!

306
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:31,639
Squat down!

307
00:12:35,039 --> 00:12:35,759
Police business!

308
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:37,960
No need to be afraid, everyone.

309
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:39,840
You're all here for matchmaking, right?

310
00:12:40,399 --> 00:12:40,759
Yes.

311
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,639
These men...

312
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,000
...are shills arranged by the matchmaking agency.

313
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,279
For a female user's first date after registering...

314
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,679
...the website arranges a meeting with...

315
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:50,480
...a man who looks pretty decent.

316
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,399
The site claims he's not interested in you...

317
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:54,120
...and suggests you buy a Gold Membership.

318
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,480
But after you pay...

319
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,320
...you end up seeing these...

320
00:12:57,919 --> 00:12:59,279
...men acting crazy and stupid.

321
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,320
Since the website arranged a meeting...

322
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:02,720
...service has technically been provided.

323
00:13:02,799 --> 00:13:04,120
So you can't request a refund.

324
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:05,720
Simply put...

325
00:13:06,279 --> 00:13:07,159
...you've all been scammed.

326
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,159
Alright.

327
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:09,200
Take them all away.

328
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,919
Miss Officer, I'm not a scammer.

329
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,679
I'm not what you think, Miss Officer.

330
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:14,480
Miss Officer!

331
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:15,360
Miss Officer!

332
00:13:15,519 --> 00:13:16,120
Miss... Miss Officer!

333
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:18,759
I... I want to ask for leave from school, Miss Officer.

334
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:20,919
Can I ask for leave from school, Miss Officer?

335
00:13:22,919 --> 00:13:23,799
This is Upland cotton.

336
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,159
Sea Island cotton.

337
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,759
Asian cotton, Levant cotton.

338
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,879
Everyone, observe carefully...

339
00:13:28,879 --> 00:13:30,600
...the morphological characteristics of different cotton species.

340
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,639
Find the patterns to distinguish them.

341
00:13:34,559 --> 00:13:35,960
Isn't this all just cotton?

342
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,720
What exactly is different?

343
00:13:38,639 --> 00:13:39,519
I can't look anymore.

344
00:13:39,919 --> 00:13:40,519
I'm going blind.

345
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,480
No need to rush, everyone.

346
00:13:42,639 --> 00:13:43,879
You can try drawing them.

347
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:46,679
Drawing is a necessary skill for agriculture students.

348
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:52,159
Sit closer if you can't see. Next time...

349
00:13:53,039 --> 00:13:54,559
...don't squint. I won't bite.

350
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:55,440
Come here.

351
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,519
You draw really well.

352
00:14:05,519 --> 00:14:06,399
Take a look, everyone.

353
00:14:06,919 --> 00:14:08,840
Student Gui Fang found the differences.

354
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:12,240
The leaves and veins are very different.

355
00:14:13,399 --> 00:14:14,080
Can you see it?

356
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,480
You're right.

357
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:16,080
Look at the diagram again.

358
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,759
You can see the difference now, right?

359
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,159
You're quite talented.

360
00:14:21,519 --> 00:14:22,480
That's amazing.

361
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:26,120
Gui Fang, you draw so well.

362
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,200
Can you teach me?

363
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:29,120
Is... is it really that good?

364
00:14:29,399 --> 00:14:30,639
Yes, yes, yes.

365
00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:32,480
You have such a talent for drawing.

366
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:34,559
Gui Fang, can you teach me how to draw the rhizomes?

367
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,039
My lab report requires us to draw the growth stage.

368
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:37,879
How do I draw that?

369
00:14:37,919 --> 00:14:39,080
I was first.

370
00:14:39,759 --> 00:14:40,320
Gui Fang.

371
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:41,559
Is this a bag?

372
00:14:41,559 --> 00:14:42,600
It's so cute.

373
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,159
I won it at the amusement park.

374
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,080
You're amazing. Fang and I caught it together.

375
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:46,600
Gui Fang.

376
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:47,240
Amazing.

377
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,360
You're so amazing.

378
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,159
Did you crochet this cup holder yourself?

379
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,200
You are just too incredible.

380
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,279
Is there anything you can't do?

381
00:14:53,279 --> 00:14:53,960
Exactly.

382
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,960
Alright, alright, classmates.

383
00:14:55,559 --> 00:14:57,120
Give our Gui Fang some space.

384
00:14:57,399 --> 00:14:58,480
Don't all crowd around here.

385
00:14:58,679 --> 00:14:59,840
Let our Fang rest for a bit.

386
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:02,440
I also have Gui Fang's class notes here.

387
00:15:02,639 --> 00:15:04,600
Gui Fang said whoever needs them can ask me.

388
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,159
Who wants them?

389
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,960
I do! Me, me, me!

390
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:07,720
I'll lend them to you.

391
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:09,320
Thanks.

392
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,120
So... so Gui Fang...

393
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:12,279
Can we borrow this to make a copy?

394
00:15:12,279 --> 00:15:12,919
Sure, sure.

395
00:15:13,159 --> 00:15:14,399
You can all take it to copy.

396
00:15:14,559 --> 00:15:16,879
It's so good to have you in our class.

397
00:15:16,879 --> 00:15:18,080
We're leaving now. Bye-bye.

398
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,360
Bye-bye. Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

399
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,240
Bye-bye. Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

400
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,320
Focus on your studies from now on.

401
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:55,480
We can't do things that break the law.

402
00:15:55,639 --> 00:15:56,679
Don't worry, Miss Officer.

403
00:15:56,679 --> 00:15:57,440
I won't dare do it again.

404
00:15:58,039 --> 00:15:59,240
H-How is it? What's the situation?

405
00:15:59,799 --> 00:16:00,960
Is this the blind date you talked about?

406
00:16:01,759 --> 00:16:02,240
No.

407
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:05,600
My cousin didn't want to come to the blind date himself.

408
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,159
So I came in his place.

409
00:16:07,279 --> 00:16:08,679
You know how my aunt is.

410
00:16:08,679 --> 00:16:09,559
She believes anything.

411
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,440
She got scammed by a fraud ring.

412
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,200
Miss Officer.

413
00:16:14,279 --> 00:16:15,639
My cousin is actually quite handsome.

414
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:16,279
About the same as me.

415
00:16:16,279 --> 00:16:17,320
How about I send you his WeChat?

416
00:16:17,399 --> 00:16:18,240
Put that away right now.

417
00:16:18,399 --> 00:16:18,919
Officer.

418
00:16:18,919 --> 00:16:20,759
So he's really okay, right?

419
00:16:21,039 --> 00:16:21,399
He's fine.

420
00:16:21,759 --> 00:16:22,360
Thank you. Thank you so much.

421
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:23,879
Are you two both his friends?

422
00:16:24,159 --> 00:16:24,720
Yes, yes, yes.

423
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:26,960
Are you busy later?

424
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:28,440
If not...

425
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:30,000
Could you help us film an anti-fraud promo video?

426
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:31,240
Sure.

427
00:16:31,639 --> 00:16:32,960
No problem, we can do it.

428
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,639
M-Miss Officer.

429
00:16:33,639 --> 00:16:34,600
If you need anything...

430
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,600
We can help anytime.

431
00:16:36,759 --> 00:16:37,120
Alright then.

432
00:16:37,879 --> 00:16:39,159
Then you play the scammer who cheats people.

433
00:16:39,919 --> 00:16:41,519
You two play the victims.

434
00:16:43,759 --> 00:16:44,480
You won't do it for free.

435
00:16:44,759 --> 00:16:46,159
After filming, everyone gets a bag of rice.

436
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:48,399
Deal.

437
00:16:48,879 --> 00:16:49,600
Scammer it is.

438
00:16:50,639 --> 00:16:51,600
I didn't think I was suitable at first.

439
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,000
You're quite suitable.

440
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:55,519
Really looks like one.

441
00:17:02,639 --> 00:17:04,079
Thanks for your hard work today.

442
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:04,599
No problem.

443
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,720
You even gave us gifts.

444
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:06,400
Thank you, thank you.

445
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:07,200
Go home early for dinner.

446
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:07,920
Okay, okay.

447
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:08,519
You.

448
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,319
Study hard from now on.

449
00:17:10,519 --> 00:17:10,960
Don't forget.

450
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:11,960
Got it, Miss Officer.

451
00:17:12,799 --> 00:17:13,599
Come visit often.

452
00:17:13,599 --> 00:17:14,079
Let's go, let's go. Okay.

453
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:15,960
That was terrible acting.

454
00:17:16,039 --> 00:17:16,759
It was indeed pretty average.

455
00:17:16,799 --> 00:17:18,039
But you acted really well, Xurui.

456
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:19,720
You're photogenic. Your acting was average too.

457
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:21,559
Why do I feel like after your amicable breakup...

458
00:17:22,039 --> 00:17:23,640
...your relationship is better than before?

459
00:17:25,599 --> 00:17:26,039
Mom.

460
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:27,640
You're back.

461
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:29,839
There's great news today.

462
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,519
We don't need to buy rice for a while.

463
00:17:31,519 --> 00:17:31,920
Let me tell you.

464
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:32,759
Thanks to Li Wai.

465
00:17:32,759 --> 00:17:33,400
They sent it over.

466
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:34,160
Where are you?

467
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:36,279
Mom.

468
00:17:39,799 --> 00:17:40,200
Mom.

469
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:44,640
You scared me.

470
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:46,039
You scared me. What are you doing?

471
00:17:46,359 --> 00:17:47,400
You didn't make a sound.

472
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,920
I've been calling you the whole time.

473
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:49,279
I said...

474
00:17:49,279 --> 00:17:50,480
Didn't hear you. I was listening to music.

475
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,000
Got some rice. It was a gift.

476
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:52,440
It's really good.

477
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,720
No need to buy rice lately. Saved money.

478
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,559
Perfect timing. We were just out of rice.

479
00:17:58,480 --> 00:17:59,359
This drawing...

480
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:00,559
How is it?

481
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:01,519
It looks just like it.

482
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:06,480
Missing a bit of soul.

483
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:09,119
I didn't draw this well.

484
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,200
It looks pretty similar.

485
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,319
What... what does this painting mean?

486
00:18:18,319 --> 00:18:19,240
Did our home change styles?

487
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,240
How is it?

488
00:18:20,559 --> 00:18:21,079
Do you like it?

489
00:18:23,079 --> 00:18:23,480
Wait a minute.

490
00:18:24,559 --> 00:18:25,200
What does this mean?

491
00:18:25,559 --> 00:18:26,359
Are you hinting at me?

492
00:18:26,839 --> 00:18:27,400
No, isn't it just...

493
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,799
I won't go to the snow mountain again. I'm not lying.

494
00:18:29,799 --> 00:18:30,960
You don't have to hang me up like a pillar of shame.

495
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,000
Isn't this mocking me?

496
00:18:32,279 --> 00:18:34,559
This is a promise between you and me.

497
00:18:35,799 --> 00:18:36,880
When you graduate,

498
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:38,440
Mom will go help you fulfill your dream.

499
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:40,000
Go to the snow mountain with you.

500
00:18:41,799 --> 00:18:43,160
It's just that lately,

501
00:18:43,279 --> 00:18:44,680
I've figured things out myself.

502
00:18:44,839 --> 00:18:46,440
You know, in this life,

503
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,960
you have to achieve something.

504
00:18:48,359 --> 00:18:49,839
You have to please yourself.

505
00:18:50,799 --> 00:18:52,359
That kind of excitement,

506
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:55,039
that drive for life.

507
00:18:55,759 --> 00:18:57,519
If you really like traveling,

508
00:18:57,839 --> 00:18:58,960
then from now on, Mom...

509
00:18:59,079 --> 00:19:00,119
Mom won't stop you anymore.

510
00:19:00,279 --> 00:19:01,599
Mom will go with you to make it happen.

511
00:19:03,279 --> 00:19:04,000
Did you...

512
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,559
plan some kind of conspiracy?

513
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,599
Are you trying to trick me?

514
00:19:07,359 --> 00:19:08,359
I've already hung the painting up.

515
00:19:08,359 --> 00:19:09,440
Would I lie to you?

516
00:19:11,039 --> 00:19:13,839
Before, I was always pretending to be young.

517
00:19:15,039 --> 00:19:16,240
But ever since that time,

518
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:17,960
after going to the amusement park with you guys,

519
00:19:18,319 --> 00:19:18,960
you know what?

520
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:22,720
I really found that feeling of being young.

521
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:25,319
That feeling that the future has many possibilities.

522
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,160
Anyway, I haven't been to a snow mountain either.

523
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,000
Let's go see it together.

524
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,480
I didn't expect that.

525
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:33,480
This amusement park had such a therapeutic effect on you.

526
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:34,960
If I knew, we would've gone sooner.

527
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:36,160
Young people also love clubbing.

528
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,119
I'll take you clubbing in a couple of days.

529
00:19:37,359 --> 00:19:38,599
What clubbing? Eat.

530
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:39,880
I see this...

531
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:40,759
painting...

532
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,559
It's pretty good. Looks quite like it.

533
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:47,359
It's not very realistic. It lacks a bit of soul.

534
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:48,559
What is this?

535
00:19:48,559 --> 00:19:49,359
This... this...

536
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:50,799
It's a draft.

537
00:19:50,799 --> 00:19:52,279
It's clumsy. Looking at it, I...

538
00:19:52,279 --> 00:19:53,000
No way.

539
00:19:53,079 --> 00:19:54,400
It's good. Definitely clumsy. It's not finished yet.

540
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,640
Wait until I finish it.

541
00:19:55,839 --> 00:19:56,759
Finished without a neck?

542
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:57,799
It's not finished!

543
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,839
Blame the teacher for running late.

544
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,079
There are no seats left in the cafeteria.

545
00:20:02,279 --> 00:20:02,759
Just right.

546
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:04,680
I can eat with my digital side dish.

547
00:20:06,839 --> 00:20:07,559
Fang, do you know?

548
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:10,319
You've become a god in everyone's hearts now.

549
00:20:10,519 --> 00:20:11,039
A top student.

550
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,319
It's not that exaggerated.

551
00:20:13,319 --> 00:20:14,200
You don't know?

552
00:20:14,599 --> 00:20:16,039
There are posts about you on the BOT.

553
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:16,720
Look.

554
00:20:20,279 --> 00:20:20,960
BOT

555
00:20:21,279 --> 00:20:21,920
Read my lips.

556
00:20:22,759 --> 00:20:23,519
BOT.

557
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:24,519
BOT.

558
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:25,279
It's from our school.

559
00:20:25,279 --> 00:20:26,400
Called Duda Gossip BOT.

560
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,880
This one. You don't follow it?

561
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:30,200
Lots of schools have one.

562
00:20:30,359 --> 00:20:32,200
Like interesting news and stories from campus.

563
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,720
Confessions and gossip all get posted there.

564
00:20:34,079 --> 00:20:34,640
You could say...

565
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:36,000
this Duda Gossip BOT...

566
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,720
is the primary source for campus gossip.

567
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:40,440
But I still prefer...

568
